# â˜ï¸ Serverless Cloud Storage

A fully serverless cloud storage web app built using AWS services. Users can sign up, log in, upload files, and view or download their uploaded files â€” all via a sleek web interface hosted on S3.

---

## ğŸš€ Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** HTML, CSS, JavaScript (Vanilla)
- **Backend:** AWS Lambda + API Gateway
- **Authentication:** Simple login/signup stored in DynamoDB
- **Storage:** Amazon S3 (Pre-Signed Upload & Download URLs)
- **Database:** Amazon DynamoDB
- **Hosting:** Static S3 Website Hosting (with optional CloudFront)

---

## âœ¨ Features

- ğŸ” User Signup/Login (stored securely in DynamoDB)
- ğŸ“¤ File Upload with real-time progress bar
- ğŸ“‚ List all uploaded files
- â¬‡ï¸ Download files via pre-signed URLs
- ğŸŒ Fully serverless (no EC2 or traditional servers)
- ğŸª„ Clean and responsive UI
- ğŸ”’ Access control using username (stored in localStorage)

